<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>閉店をお考えの方へ | BRIDGE CYCLE</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@200;300;400;700&family=Shippori+Mincho+B1:wght@400;500;700;800&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300;1,400&family=IM+Fell+English:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --navy:     #0D1B2A;
  --navy-mid: #132033;
  --navy-lt:  #1E3350;
  --gold:     #C9A84C;
  --gold-lt:  #E2C47A;
  --gold-dim: #8A7040;
  --cream:    #F7F2E8;
  --cream-dk: #EDE6D4;
  --smoke:    #C8BEAA;
  --warm:     #7A6A52;
  --rust:     #B85C38;
  --sage:     #3D5A4C;
  --white:    #FFFFFF;
  --r: 0.6rem;
}

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; scroll-padding-top: 80px; }

body {
  background: var(--cream);
  color: var(--navy);
  font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
  overflow-x: hidden;
  line-height: 1.85;
}

::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--cream-dk); }
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--gold-dim); }

/* ── NAV ── */
nav {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 200;
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  padding: 18px 48px;
  background: rgba(247,242,232,0.92);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
}
.nav-logo {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  color: var(--navy); text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase;
}
.nav-logo em { color: var(--gold); font-style: normal; }
.nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; align-items: center; }
.nav-links a {
  font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--warm);
  text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s;
}
.nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }
.nav-cta {
  font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  background: var(--navy); color: var(--gold) !important;
  padding: 10px 24px; border: none;
  transition: all 0.3s !important;
}
.nav-cta:hover { background: var(--gold) !important; color: var(--navy) !important; }

/* ── HERO ── */
.hero {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.hero-left {
  background: var(--navy);
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
  padding: 120px 72px 72px 72px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.hero-left::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  width: 500px; height: 500px; border-radius: 50%;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
  top: -150px; right: -200px;
}
.hero-left::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  width: 280px; height: 280px; border-radius: 50%;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.08);
  bottom: 60px; left: -80px;
}

.hero-eyebrow {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
  font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
  animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease both;
}
.hero-eyebrow::before {
  content: ''; display: block;
  width: 36px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold-dim); flex-shrink: 0;
}

.hero-title {
  font-family: 'Shippori Mincho B1', serif;
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.6vw, 3rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1.35;
  color: var(--cream);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.1s ease both;
}
.hero-title em {
  display: block;
  font-style: normal;
  color: var(--gold);
  font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.7vw, 1.35rem);
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  border-left: 2px solid var(--gold-dim);
  padding-left: 14px;
}

.hero-subtitle {
  font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--smoke); line-height: 2.1;
  max-width: 460px;
  animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.2s ease both;
}
.hero-subtitle strong { color: var(--gold-lt); }
.hero-subtitle p { margin-bottom: 14px; }
.hero-subtitle p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

.hero-btns {
  display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-top: 48px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.3s ease both;
}
.btn-primary {
  display: inline-block;
  background: var(--gold); color: var(--navy);
  font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  padding: 16px 36px; text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 700; font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
  transition: all 0.3s;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.btn-primary::after { content: '→'; position: absolute; right: -20px; transition: right 0.3s; }
.btn-primary:hover { padding-right: 52px; background: var(--gold-lt); }
.btn-primary:hover::after { right: 16px; }
.btn-ghost {
  display: inline-block;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.4); color: var(--smoke);
  font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  padding: 16px 32px; text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.3s;
}
.btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }

.hero-right {
  background: var(--cream-dk);
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
  align-items: center; padding: 120px 60px 80px;
  position: relative;
}

/* Cost comparison card */
.cost-card {
  background: var(--white);
  border: 1px solid rgba(13,27,42,0.1);
  padding: 40px;
  box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(13,27,42,0.08);
  width: 100%; max-width: 380px;
  animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.3s ease both;
}
.cost-card-label {
  font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--warm);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
}
.cost-card-label::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--cream-dk); }
.cost-row {
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline;
  padding: 12px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--cream-dk);
}
.cost-row:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }
.cost-item-name { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--warm); }
.cost-before {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--rust);
  text-decoration: line-through;
  opacity: 0.7;
}
.cost-after {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--sage);
}
.cost-unit { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--smoke); margin-left: 4px; }
.cost-total-row {
  margin-top: 20px;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  background: rgba(61,90,76,0.06);
  border: 1px solid rgba(61,90,76,0.15);
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
}
.cost-total-label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--sage); font-weight: 700; }
.cost-total-val {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 2rem; color: var(--sage); font-weight: 400;
}
.cost-note {
  font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--smoke); margin-top: 12px; line-height: 1.8;
}

/* ── SECTION BASE ── */
section { padding: 100px 0; }
.container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 48px; }

.sec-label {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.35em; color: var(--gold-dim);
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.sec-label::after { content: ''; flex: 1; max-width: 60px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold-dim); }

.sec-title {
  font-family: 'Shippori Mincho B1', serif;
  font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.8vw, 2.4rem);
  font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.4;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.sec-lead {
  font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--warm); line-height: 2;
  max-width: 640px; margin-bottom: 56px;
}

/* ── PAIN SECTION ── */
.pain-section { background: var(--navy-mid); }
.pain-section .sec-title { color: var(--cream); }
.pain-section .sec-lead { color: var(--smoke); }
.pain-section .sec-label { color: var(--gold-dim); }

.pain-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 2px;
  margin-top: 0;
}
.pain-card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  padding: 40px 32px;
  border-top: 2px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
  position: relative;
}
.pain-num {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
  position: absolute; top: 20px; right: 24px;
  line-height: 1;
}
.pain-icon {
  width: 44px; height: 44px; margin-bottom: 20px;
  background: rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
}
.pain-title {
  font-family: 'Shippori Mincho B1', serif;
  font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--cream);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.pain-body {
  font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--smoke); line-height: 2;
}
.pain-figure {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--rust);
  margin-top: 14px; display: block;
}

/* ── SOLUTION SECTION ── */
.solution-inner {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 72px; align-items: center;
}
.solution-visual {
  position: relative;
}
.solution-diagram {
  width: 100%;
}
.solution-text .sec-lead { margin-bottom: 32px; }
.solution-list { list-style: none; }
.solution-list li {
  display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start;
  padding: 16px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.12);
  font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.9;
}
.solution-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.solution-list .check {
  width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(61,90,76,0.1);
  border: 1px solid var(--sage);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 4px;
  font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--sage);
}

/* ── FLOW SECTION ── */
.flow-section { background: var(--navy-mid); }
.flow-section .sec-title { color: var(--cream); }
.flow-section .sec-lead { color: var(--smoke); }
.flow-section .sec-label { color: var(--gold-dim); }

.flow-steps {
  display: flex; gap: 0; align-items: stretch;
  margin-top: 56px;
}
.flow-step {
  flex: 1;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  padding: 36px 28px;
  position: relative;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
}
.flow-step:not(:last-child)::after {
  content: '→';
  position: absolute; right: -14px; top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  font-size: 1rem; color: var(--gold-dim);
  z-index: 1; background: var(--navy-mid);
  padding: 4px;
}
.flow-step-num {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  color: var(--gold-dim); margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.flow-step-title {
  font-family: 'Shippori Mincho B1', serif;
  font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 10px;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.flow-step-body { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--smoke); line-height: 1.9; }
.flow-step.highlight { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.08); border-top-color: var(--gold); }
.flow-step.highlight .flow-step-title { color: var(--gold-lt); }

/* ── FREE SECTION ── */
.free-section { background: var(--cream-dk); }
.free-inner {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 72px; align-items: center;
}
.free-badge {
  text-align: center; padding: 60px 48px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(13,27,42,0.08);
  background: var(--white);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(13,27,42,0.06);
}
.free-badge-label {
  font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.3em; color: var(--warm); margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.free-badge-num {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 6rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--sage);
  line-height: 1;
}
.free-badge-unit { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--sage); margin-top: 4px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; }
.free-badge-desc {
  margin-top: 24px; font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--warm); line-height: 2;
}
.free-badge-rule {
  margin-top: 20px; padding: 14px 20px;
  background: rgba(61,90,76,0.06);
  border: 1px solid rgba(61,90,76,0.12);
  font-size: 0.73rem; color: var(--sage); line-height: 1.9;
}
.free-text .sec-lead { margin-bottom: 32px; }

/* ── FIGURE STYLES ── */
.fig-frame { margin-top: 48px; border: 1px solid var(--line,rgba(255,255,255,0.1)); overflow: hidden; }
.fig-frame svg { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }
.fig-caption { font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--smoke); padding: 12px 24px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); background: rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
.fig-frame.fig-light { border-color: rgba(13,27,42,0.1); }
.fig-frame.fig-light .fig-caption { background: var(--cream-dk); color: var(--warm); border-color: rgba(13,27,42,0.06); }

/* ── VOICE SECTION ── */
.voice-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 24px;
}
.voice-card {
  background: var(--white);
  border: 1px solid rgba(13,27,42,0.06);
  padding: 36px;
  position: relative;
}
.voice-card::before {
  content: '\201C';
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 4rem; color: rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
  position: absolute; top: 16px; left: 20px;
  line-height: 1;
}
.voice-quote {
  font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 2; color: var(--navy);
  margin-bottom: 20px; padding-top: 16px;
}
.voice-quote strong { color: var(--sage); }
.voice-meta {
  font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--smoke); letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: center;
}
.voice-meta::before { content: '—'; }
.voice-tag {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--warm);
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3); padding: 3px 10px;
  margin-right: 8px;
}

/* ── CTA SECTION ── */
.cta-section {
  background: var(--navy);
  text-align: center; padding: 120px 48px;
}
.cta-eyebrow {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.4em; color: var(--gold-dim);
  margin-bottom: 24px; text-transform: uppercase;
}
.cta-title {
  font-family: 'Shippori Mincho B1', serif;
  font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
  font-weight: 800; color: var(--cream);
  line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.cta-sub {
  font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--smoke); max-width: 560px;
  margin: 0 auto 48px; line-height: 2;
}
.cta-btns { display: flex; gap: 20px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.cta-btn-main {
  display: inline-block;
  background: var(--gold); color: var(--navy);
  font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; font-weight: 700;
  font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
  padding: 20px 56px; text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.3s;
}
.cta-btn-main:hover { background: var(--gold-lt); }
.cta-free-note {
  margin-top: 20px;
  font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--smoke); letter-spacing: 0.12em;
}

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer {
  background: var(--navy);
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
  padding: 48px;
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
}
.footer-logo {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 0.9rem; letter-spacing: 0.3em; color: var(--gold-dim);
  text-decoration: none;
}
.footer-copy { font-size: 0.65rem; color: rgba(200,190,170,0.4); letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
.footer-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; }
.footer-links a { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--smoke); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
.footer-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }

/* ── REVEAL ── */
.reveal {
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px);
  transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
}
.reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
}
@keyframes fadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; }
}

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .hero-right { display: none; }
  .hero-left { padding: 120px 32px 72px; min-height: 100vh; }
  .solution-inner, .free-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
  .pain-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .flow-steps { flex-direction: column; }
  .flow-step:not(:last-child)::after { display: none; }
  .voice-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  nav { padding: 16px 24px; }
  .nav-links { display: none; }
  .container { padding: 0 24px; }
  footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; text-align: center; }
  .hero-btns { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
  .cta-btns { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ── NAV ── -->
<nav>
  <a href="index.html" class="nav-logo">Bridge <em>&</em> Cycle</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="index.html">管理会社の方へ</a>
    <a href="lp.html">創業希望者の方へ</a>
    <a href="exit.html">閉店をお考えの方へ</a>
    <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">無料相談</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ── HERO ── -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-left">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">閉店をお考えの飲食店・小売店オーナーへ</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      <em>原状回復費用、<br>払わなくていいかもしれません。</em>
      閉める前に、<br>一度だけ話してください。
    </h1>
    <div class="hero-subtitle">
      <p>スケルトン戻し工事には、<strong>100〜300万円以上</strong>かかることがあります。それが不要になる可能性があります。</p>
      <p>BRIDGE CYCLEは、設備・内装をそのまま活かせる次の開業者を探します。引き継ぎが成立すれば、<strong>原状回復工事が不要</strong>になる場合があります。</p>
      <p>退店希望者への費用は<strong>一切かかりません</strong>。管理会社・物件オーナー側が負担する仕組みです。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">まず、話してみる（無料）</a>
      <a href="#flow" class="btn-ghost">相談の流れを見る</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-right">
    <div class="cost-card">
      <div class="cost-card-label">費用の比較（イメージ）</div>
      <div class="cost-row">
        <span class="cost-item-name">スケルトン撤去工事</span>
        <span>
          <span class="cost-before">150万<span class="cost-unit">円〜</span></span>
          <span class="cost-after"> → 0<span class="cost-unit">円</span></span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-row">
        <span class="cost-item-name">厨房機器の処分費用</span>
        <span>
          <span class="cost-before">30万<span class="cost-unit">円〜</span></span>
          <span class="cost-after"> → 0<span class="cost-unit">円</span></span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-row">
        <span class="cost-item-name">内装撤去・廃材処分</span>
        <span>
          <span class="cost-before">40万<span class="cost-unit">円〜</span></span>
          <span class="cost-after"> → 0<span class="cost-unit">円</span></span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-total-row">
        <span class="cost-total-label">あなたの負担</span>
